lead_paragraph: When the U.S. Open began Ryan Harrison was one half of a Flushing Meadows feel good story as he and younger brother Christian become the first siblings to come through qualifying into a grand slam main draw.

headline.print_headline: Harrison Goes From U.S. Open Sideshow to Headliner With Win
